      "span_text": "The D values obtained in this work for the tested strains were lower than the D values previously reported for the strain of Lb. rhamnosus E 800 and Lb. salivarius UCC 500 [CITATION_1] , and they were higher than the values previously reported for Lb. salivarius UCC 118 at 61˚C (Gardnier et al., 2000) .",
